# PredictIQ Ingestion Catalog

This document lists all active ingestion scripts, their target data sources, and the resulting Bronze layer storage locations.

| Script Name | Data Source | Frequency | Output (Bronze Layer) | Description |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| [gdelt_events_ingest.py](file:///c:/Data%20Engineering/codeprep/predection_project/native_ingestion/gdelt_events_ingest.py) | GDELT 2.0 Events | 15 mins | `data/bronze/gdelt/gdelt_events` | Ingests structured "actor-action" records filtered for political events. |
| `flat_gdelt_gkg_ingest.py` | GDELT 2.0 GKG | 15 mins | `data/bronze/gdelt/gdelt_gkg` | Ingests themes, entities (V2Persons), and tone from the global news cycle. |
| `flat_reuters_news_ingest.py` | Reuters Politics (RSS) | Periodic | `data/bronze/reuters` | Scrapes full-text political news articles for RAG context. |
| `flat_nyt_news_ingest.py` | NYT Politics (RSS) | Periodic | `data/bronze/nyt` | Scrapes full-text political news articles for RAG context. |
| `flat_kalshi_markets_active.py`| Kalshi API (V2) | Real-time/Poll | `data/bronze/kalshi_markets/open`| Ingests currently open political prediction markets. |
| `flat_kalshi_daily_settlement.py`| Kalshi API (V2) | Daily | `data/bronze/kalshi_markets/settled`| Ingests historically settled/resolved markets. |

---

## Reference Data
| File Name | Storage Path | Description |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| `cameo_eventcodes.csv` | `reference/` | Translates EventRootCodes to labels. |
| `fips_countries.csv` | `reference/` | Translates country codes to nation names. |
| `cameo_actortypes.csv` | `reference/` | Translates ActorType codes (GOV, MIL). |
| `cameo_quadclass.csv` | `reference/` | High-level event category mapping. |
